u</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%BA/Phan-B%C3%A2n-L%C3%A3o-xu%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BA%ADp-s%E1%BB%95-thi-giai-h%E1%BB%AFu-ho%C3%A0i-T%C3%B4-%C4%90am-Ch%C3%A2u-gi%E1%BA%A3-nh%C3%A2n-ph%C3%BA-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-onz9pQ7NmqjF2VXTwIvF-Q">Phan Bân Lão xuất thập sổ thi giai hữu hoài Tô Đam Châu giả nhân phú nhị thủ kỳ 1 - 潘豳老出十數詩皆有懷蘇儋州者因賦二首其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%BA/author-kEtJEG_ZpvOqTp5qubCKUQ">Hạ Chú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4n/Quan-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Bi-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-vzEuhbEBbdeLag4po7h6IQ">Quan Đại Bi tự - 觀大悲寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4n/author-YDc3orDW4enWycHMfed3Ww">Lê Quý Đôn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Thi%C3%AAn-Giang-ng%E1%BB%A5c/poem-F9kEmgeXSKkzCY_9dPVvwg">Thiên Giang ngục - 遷江獄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%A0nh-T%C3%B4n-Du%E1%BA%ADt/T%C6%B0-Vi%E1%BB%87t-nh%C3%A2n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81-D%C6%B0-th%E1%BB%8B-n%E1%BB%AF-t%E1%BB%AD-t%C3%BA-T%C3%A2y-T%E1%BB%AD-ho%C3%A1n-sa-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-Tr%C3%ACnh-Th%C3%B4n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-t%C3%A1c/poem-oOnbkgruwwr0rIDonOZkSw">Tư Việt nhân - Đề Dư thị nữ tử tú Tây Tử hoán sa đồ, đồng Trình Thôn, Nguyễn Đình tác - 思越人－題余氏女子繡西子浣紗圖，同程村、阮亭作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%A0nh-T%C3%B4n-Du%E1%BA%ADt/author-nP1V-tl_i1mwn2BJ9gSE-g">Bành Tôn Duật</a>)<br></div>	</div>
